<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{newsletterTitle}} - {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header .issue {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .article {
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .article-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .article-meta {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .article-excerpt {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .read-more {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .read-more:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #dee2e6, transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .stats-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            display: block;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .quick-links {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .quick-links h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .quick-links ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .quick-links li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .quick-links a {
            color: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .quick-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #adb5bd;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #adb5bd;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{newsletterTitle}}</h1>
            <div class="issue">Issue #{{issueNumber}} â€¢ {{issueDate}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{firstName}}! ðŸ‘‹
            </div>
            
            <p>Welcome to this {{period}} edition of {{newsletterTitle}}! We've got some exciting updates, insights, and resources to share with you.</p>
            
            {{#each articles}}
            <div class="article">
                <div class="article-meta">{{category}} â€¢ {{readTime}} min read</div>
                <div class="article-title">{{title}}</div>
                <div class="article-excerpt">{{excerpt}}</div>
                <a href="{{url}}" class="read-more">Read full article â†’</a>
            </div>
            {{#unless @last}}<div class="divider"></div>{{/unless}}
            {{/each}}
            
            <div class="stats-section">
                <h3>This Month's Highlights</h3>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">{{stats.newUsers}}</span>
                        <div class="stat-label">New Users</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">{{stats.articles}}</span>
                        <div class="stat-label">Articles Published</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">{{stats.engagement}}%</span>
                        <div class="stat-label">Engagement</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="quick-links">
                <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                <ul>
                    {{#each quickLinks}}
                    <li><a href="{{url}}">{{title}}</a></li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>As always, we'd love to hear your feedback! Reply to this email or reach out to us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
            
            <p>
                Best regards,<br>
                The {{companyName}} Team
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="{{socialLinks.twitter}}">Twitter</a>
                <a href="{{socialLinks.linkedin}}">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="{{socialLinks.facebook}}">Facebook</a>
            </div>
            <p>
                {{companyName}} | {{address}}<br>
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                <a href="{{preferencesUrl}}">Email Preferences</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
